\layout Subsection

The Game
\layout Paragraph

Metropolis is a mission based Action RPG.
\layout Subsection

Overview
\layout Paragraph

In Metropolis, a team of mercenaries executes vicarious missions in different
 settings.
 The missions range from robbery, information retrieval, assassination,
 and protection.
 Each of the mercenaries have different skills which are all necessary to
 complete the missions thus requiring them to work together as a team.
\layout Subsection

Background
\layout Paragraph

Metropolis takes place in a futuristic Hawaii that features cities both
 above and below water.
 The cities feature dome style buildings with 1930's dome cars.
 In the world of Metropolis, corporations have gained power that rivals
 the government's, and in some cases, surpasses it.
 The corporations have separate and often conflicting goals with both each
 other and the government.
 Due to the increased technology of the media, the corporations must keep
 a very low profile with any and all 
